<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3904.3.8>
    bibo:endPage "426" ;
    bibo:issue "3" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "421" ;
    bibo:volume "3904" ;
    dc:creator "Sasamoto, Akihiko" ;
    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "Anigosomphus yanagisawai sp. nov., a new gomphid dragonfly from northern Thailand (Odonata: Anisoptera: Gomphidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231866>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231867>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231868> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231866>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 2. Anisogomphus yanagisawai sp. nov., holotype male (1) and paratype female (2), general habitus. (Bar: 1 cm)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/231866/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231867>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3 – 10. Anisogomphus yanagisawai sp. nov., holotype male (3 – 9) and paratype female (10): (3) head; (4) thorax; (5) anal appendages in lateral view; (6) the same in dorsal view; (7) accessory genitalia, lateral view; (8) penile organ in lateral view; (9) the distal two segments of penile organ in dorsal view; (10) Valvula vulvae in ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/231867/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231868>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 – 12. The sites where Anisogomphus yanagisawai sp. nov. were collected. (11) A paved road besides a running stream, where the male settled on leaves of roadside trees; (12) a stream which the female visited for oviposition. (Photo by Mr Ya nag isa wa)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/231868/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

